flowchart TD
  A[Open source PDF] --> B[Extract text and image objects]
  B --> C[Classify lines by role]
  C --> D[Build TranslationUnit records]
  D --> E[Translate with term decisions]
  E --> F[Build LayoutSlot records]
  F --> G[Apply text redactions]
  G --> H[Insert Chinese title and timeline text]
  H --> I[Cover visual-only English]
  I --> J[Render PNG]
  J --> K[Compute machine checks]
  K --> L[Compute visual occupancy metrics]
  L --> M{Thresholds pass?}
  M -->|yes| N[Accept output PDF]
  M -->|text residue| O[Repair translation]
  M -->|overflow| P[Repair layout slot]
  M -->|gap or area ratio| Q[Repair line count or translation length]
  M -->|tight typography| R[Repair font size and line height]
  M -->|collision| S[Repair body_x/body_w]
  O --> F
  P --> F
  Q --> F
  R --> F
  S --> F
